document_data.name: Anfalen
document_data.mainbody: '''Anfalen''' was a wry and good-humored [[moon elf]] [[high mage]] in [[Evermeet]].
document_data.History: In [[1374 DR]], after the failed [[fey'ri invasion of Evereska]], Anfalen was among the high mages who summoned [[Araevin Teshurr]] to explain about it.
